        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/theark/scene_magpie.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 2de3e84f-4853-4d7a-abc0-bd4e005c71bd).Image",
        "Description": "47, We have situation that needs to be dealt. I will send you briefing shortly. Alright so your target is Malcolm Hughes. Smart and can nearly get away with every crime she does. Isle of Sg&#224;il is hosting special event and invite few special guests. Blake Nathinal is weathly and has a lot of value items that he shows off. Malcolm Hughes is planning to steal some of the value items in the showroom later tonight. We also know she has hired few people to blend in as guards scoping the area to plan the steal of the values. She as well undercover and trying to sabotage security system in the showroom from her laptop. Blake is aware of the situation and has hired us to take care off them. I will say 47 that this will be dangerous mission but i am aware what your capable off doing. You will arrive there shortly. I will leave to prepare. Good Luck 47.",
